HEADWORD: Intersomnious
<hw>In`ter*som"ni*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>inter-</ets> + L. <ets>somnus</ets> sleep.]</ety> <def>Between the
times of sleeping; in an interval of wakefulness.</def>
